</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="76.[151,1437,151,645]" pageId="76" pageNumber="77">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,413,582,609]" pageId="76" pageNumber="77">Notes on bionomy</emphasis>
. According to 
